knows the game inside and out?

226
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:41,161
Who knows how to teach kids to
become honorable, accountable men

227
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,600
with self-worth?

228
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:47,050
