In Luke 6:38,

297
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:40,411
Luke says,
"Give and it will be given to you.

298
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:44,328
Good measure, pressed down,
shaken together and running over

299
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:46,488
