300
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:51,447
For with the measure you use,
it will be measured to you."

301
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:55,562
Any idea what Luke is saying here?
Arturo?

302
00:17:57,040 --> 00:17:58,201
You reap what you sow.

303
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:01,449
Like, whatever you do, good or bad,
comes back to you.

304
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,921
Anyone else think you give to others

305
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:07,169
and the blessing is returned
in equal measure?

306
00:18:07,600 --> 00:18:09,090
Salinas.

307
