You ain't in line to be starting
quarterback on the streak team

311
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:22,802
because you've done the right thing.

312
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,968
It's because you're 6'2"
with a cannon for an arm.

313
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:29,563
GUYS: Ha, ha, ha.
So, Tayshon, what do you believe?

314
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:34,249
Well, down where I sleep, the dealers
in Richmond make mad money.

315
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:37,967
My aunt was an ER nurse.
Worked her whole life helping people.

316
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:41,004
Time came for her to get hers,
they up and fired her,

317
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,680
six months
before they gotta pay her retirement.

318
00:18:44,120 --> 00:18:47,806
Dog-eat-dog, yo. Take what you need.
They don't care how good you've been.

319
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:51,891
You sitting around waiting for somebody
to pay you back, you going hungry.

320
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:56,961
So why does a guy like Luke, who's a
doctor, painter, writer, historian,

321
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,527
take the time to invent a lie?

322
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:01,086
It ain't a lie.

323
00:19:01,840 --> 00:19:05,640
Your pops dies, five-0 puts your mom
on trial for it when, oops,

324
00:19:05,840 --> 00:19:07,842
our bad, the shipyard poisoned him.

325
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:11,084
Pressure gives her a stroke
and now she ain't got long.

326
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:13,169
Easy. Everyone knows the story.

327
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:15,366
So tell me, homey.

328
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:17,960
You really been that bad
to deserve all that's come your way?

329
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,411
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

330
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:21,446
