363
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:10,245
Well, family isn't just blood relatives.

364
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:14,208
It's anyone
who loves you unconditionally.

365
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:17,042
<i>♪♪♪</i>

366
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:21,970
"To Coach Lad,

367
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:26,681
