379
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,448
I'm alone.

380
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:07,927
I got nobody left.

381
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,526
No, you're not.

382
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,888
You've got Jamal...

383
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:15,531
