384
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,365
[CAR DOOR LOCK CHIRPS]

385
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:43,685
<i>♪♪♪</i>

386
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:30,365
BEV: I'm just gonna nap for
10 more minutes, then get up.

387
00:23:37,120 --> 00:23:39,248
Don't snore.

388
00:23:42,720 --> 00:23:44,768
[SNORTING]

389
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:47,207
I'm not laughing.

390
00:23:47,600 --> 00:23:49,602
[SNORTING
AND GRUNTING]

391
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:52,406
What did I ever see in you? Bob?

392
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:54,204
Bob? Bob?

393
00:23:55,280 --> 00:23:57,521
Bob, Bob, please. Bob? Bob?

394
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,290
Danny!

395
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:01,721
Bob, what's going on?
Bob? Oh, my God, Bob!

396
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:03,644
Danny!
Yeah, Mom.

397
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:05,888
