Danny!

398
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:09,651
Mom, what's wrong?
Danny, please call 911!

399
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,962
Oh, my God! Call 911!
Mom! Morn!

400
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:16,450
Dad? Where is the phone? It's not here.
Danny, tell them it's a seizure.

401
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:18,762
Find the phone!
Where is it?

402
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:24,127
Oh, my God. Look at me.
Look in my eyes. Look in my eyes.

403
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:27,130
Oh, my God, you okay?
You okay? Breathe.

404
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:34,051
[CHATTERING]

405
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:42,369
MAN 1: Hey, Amani. Thanks for coming.
MAN 2: Hey, Amani.

406
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:45,964
MAN 3: Oh, one for me. Just one second.
AMANI: Cool.

407
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:48,527
Hey. Who's in there?

408
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:52,645
Currently paying his respects to
the coach, Maurice Jones Drew.

409
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,730
No way.

410
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:58,322
