This really scared him.

436
00:26:15,840 --> 00:26:17,251
It's a lie.

437
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,765
<i>♪♪♪</i>

438
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:20,041
What is?

439
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:25,205
Me. I got caught up in work
and the streak and let it nearly kill me.

440
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:28,171
