441
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:31,921
commit to each other, your teachers,
your friends, your family.

442
00:26:32,120 --> 00:26:34,009
Was I committed to you?

443
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,601
Was I committed to my children?

444
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:40,725
I've been a lousy husband
and the worst dad.

445
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:45,801
Danny's not angry because he isn't
getting the chance to play for you.

446
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:50,764
He's angry because he wants
a chance to know you.

447
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:55,647
What do I do now?

448
00:26:57,240 --> 00:27:01,211
Spend as much time with your family
as you do the team.

449
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:09,448
WOMAN: See you later, babe.
