that just ain't a jersey, man.

515
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:05,129
It's an answered prayer.

516
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:07,643
Look at me, dog.

517
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,890
You and me.

518
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:18,167
Brothers for life, dog.

519
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:23,364
Come on.

520
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:26,048
<i>♪♪♪</i>

521
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:33,249
Brothers for life.

522
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:37,365
