to continue to give a perfect effort,

533
00:32:35,360 --> 00:32:37,169
every game.

534
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:44,646
[TRUMPET TOOTING]

535
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:56,402
Not your typical trumpet number, huh?

536
00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:58,648
No, not typical. Heh, heh.
Heh, heh.

537
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:01,368
Getting the hang of it?

538
00:33:01,560 --> 00:33:04,450
Me or Michael?
You.

539
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:07,171
[LAUGHS]

540
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:09,368
Anything else I can help you with?

541
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:10,971
Uh, no.

542
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:13,043
Think you're doing great.

543
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:16,130
Just remember,
I like mine rare.

544
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,804
You got it.

545
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:30,966
[WHISTLE BLOWS ON TV]

546
00:33:31,120 --> 00:33:34,806
