Yeah, sure.

547
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:37,002
[CHATTERING ON TV]

548
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:44,882
I've dropped more passes this summer
than the previous three years combined.

549
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:51,041
BOB: You're not seeing the
ball into your hands.

550
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:54,801
You're looking up-field before you catch.
I know.

551
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:57,527
I try to stop, but...

552
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,081
What should I do?

553
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,807
You gotta work on that
with Coach Alumbaugh.

554
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:06,567
I don't need Coach Alumbaugh.

555
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:07,807
I need you.

556
00:34:10,240 --> 00:34:12,891
My senior season is here, Dad.
My last shot.

557
00:34:13,080 --> 00:34:15,242
Danny, I'm not your coach.

558
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:18,364
But I wanna spend
some time together, get closer.

559
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:21,291
I found a river-rafting outfit...
River rafting?

560
00:34:21,480 --> 00:34:24,324
Afterwards, we'll win
the father-son three-legged race.

561
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:28,081
This is perfect. The whole time
I needed a father, I got a coach.

562
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:32,001
And now I need a coach
and all I've got is a lame dad.

563
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,848
Exercise?

564
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:42,088
Running again.

565
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:48,051
How are my test scores?
Better than expected.

566
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:52,248
Your heart has made an unusually
strong recovery, Mr. Ladouceur.

567
00:34:52,720 --> 00:34:56,008
You're free to return
to normal activities.

568
00:34:56,720 --> 00:34:57,960
Coaching?

569
00:34:59,240 --> 00:35:02,164
Keep the stress down,
but, yes.

570
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:03,526
<i>♪♪♪</i>

571
00:35:04,120 --> 00:35:05,724
[SIGHS]

572
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:09,284
Wow, that's great.
It must be such a relief.

573
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:11,164
Yeah.

574
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:15,411
She, uh,
said I could go back to coaching.

575
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:20,922
So is that your plan, Bob?

576
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:28,850
We'll see.

577
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,441
Hey-

578
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,651
What's that?

579
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:34,887
What?

580
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,366
Smells good.
Heh, heh.

581
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:39,006
Me or the sauce?

582
00:35:39,240 --> 00:35:40,924
The sauce.

583
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:43,646
I was hoping it was me.
Heh, heh, heh.

584
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:46,761
MAN:
Ready, and go.

585
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,770
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

586
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:53,601
[PLAYERS GRUNTING]

587
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:56,566
