Hey, butt kicks.

588
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:58,529
Ready, up.

589
00:35:58,760 --> 00:35:59,841
You're late.

590
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,885
Yeah, I been busy.

591
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:05,482
Well, that explains yesterday.
You missed an entire practice.

592
00:36:05,720 --> 00:36:08,291
I got a note from the nurse,
little Lad.

593
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:11,649
How insensitive of us, Chris.
He had a tummy ache.

594
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:14,161
