I'll drop you.

595
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:16,482
Ha, ha. Now, that's funny.

596
00:36:16,680 --> 00:36:19,684
Nobody misses practice
without clearing it with the captain.

597
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:24,488
Well, I ain't nobody.
On JV, man, I played both ways.

598
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:28,844
Caught 38 passes and five picks.
How much practice do I need?

599
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:32,163
It's not about
It's about us. This team.

600
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:34,761
Both of y'all can go ahead
and kiss my...

601
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,729
Push me? Team?

602
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:41,329
Ain't no team! Truth is, it comes down
to four or five of us bringing our game!

603
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:45,445
Say what you want, Chris, Danny. This
team thing don't mean nothing now!

604
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:47,011
Back off!
TERRY: Hey, hold up!

605
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:49,407
