you'll have to scrap for everything.

607
00:36:53,600 --> 00:36:57,366
Wanna be a scrappy team?
You're gonna have to respect each other.

608
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,125
Now, get back to practice.

609
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,200
High kicks.

610
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:09,324
[WHISTLE BLOWS]

611
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:14,602
[CHATTERING]

612
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:17,720
<i>♪♪♪</i>

613
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:20,127
<i>♪ Tell me, who do it better? ♪</i>

614
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,884
♪ What? What? ♪
♪ Who do it <i>better?</i> ♪

