00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:57,324
First thing tomorrow,
man.

629
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:59,045
Don't forget about us, homes.

630
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:01,846
Course not, baby.
Of course not. Come on.

631
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:04,168
Man, all y'all horrible!

