653
00:39:13,240 --> 00:39:14,969
<i>♪ This is how we do it ♪</i>

654
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:18,403
♪ Mm-ah-mm-ah-mm-ah-oh ♪

655
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:22,042
