00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,526
LANDRIN:
Mama, you stay here.

675
00:40:25,560 --> 00:40:27,050
T-GRAM:
Oh, God.

676
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:32,722
LANDRIN:
Jesus Christ. No, no.

677
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:35,400
