688
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:14,491
<i>♪ Hold on, help is on the way ♪</i>

689
00:41:14,680 --> 00:41:18,401
<i>♪ God hasn't forgotten you ♪</i>

690
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:23,730
