00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:44,081
MINISTER: And without further
ado, Coach Bob Ladouceur.

695
00:41:46,120 --> 00:41:48,771
[SOBBING]

696
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:55,200
Thank you, Coach Ladouceur.

697
00:41:58,600 --> 00:42:00,125
Minister.

698
00:42:04,160 --> 00:42:07,562
I remember the first time I saw T.K.

699
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:09,364
He was that...

700
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:15,040
awkward freshman, all arms and legs,
