701
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:20,286
A coach couldn't help
but notice the smooth grace of his...

702
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:24,168
athletic ability.

703
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:30,810
<i>♪♪♪</i>

